    "multicolumn_gGnB8U": {
      "type": "multicolumn",
      "blocks": {
        "column_b9C7km": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/New_Project_3.png",
            "title": "embracing every self",
            "text": "<p>At Revu, we believe in celebrating and supporting every individual's journey towards self-love and acceptance, affirming that true beauty lies in embracing one's authentic self.<\/p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "column_tCfnyw": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/New_Project_3.png",
            "title": "strength in vulnerability",
            "text": "<p>We hold the conviction that acknowledging and sharing our vulnerabilities is a powerful step towards healing. Our commitment extends beyond skincare, supporting mental wellness and resilience in the face of body dysmorphia.<\/p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "column_ye4iNb": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/New_Project_3.png",
            "title": "unity in diversity ",
            "text": "<p>Revu is built on the principle that diversity is our strength. We stand in solidarity with all those navigating body dysmorphia, advocating for a world where everyone feels seen, valued, and empowered in their unique beauty.<\/p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        }
      },
